提示
我们知道在MySQL可以通过...order by field()函数自定义排序，格式：field(字段名,str1,str2,str3,str4)，按照str1、str2、str3、str4顺序返回。那么在php如何实现

实现：function orderByField($data, $field, $sort)  
&#123;  
    $keys &#x3D; array_reduce($data, function ($result, $v) use ($field, $sort) &#123;  
        $result[] &#x3D; array_search($v[$field], $sort);  
        return $result;  
    &#125;);    
    array_multisort($keys, $data);  
    return $data;  
&#125;
例子：$data&#x3D;[
    [&#39;name&#39;&#x3D;&gt;&#39;a&#39;,&#39;age&#39;&#x3D;&gt;10],
    [&#39;name&#39;&#x3D;&gt;&#39;b&#39;,&#39;age&#39;&#x3D;&gt;20],
    [&#39;name&#39;&#x3D;&gt;&#39;c&#39;,&#39;age&#39;&#x3D;&gt;30],
    [&#39;name&#39;&#x3D;&gt;&#39;d&#39;,&#39;age&#39;&#x3D;&gt;40],
    [&#39;name&#39;&#x3D;&gt;&#39;e&#39;,&#39;age&#39;&#x3D;&gt;50]
];
$sort &#x3D; [10,30,20,50,40];
$data &#x3D; orderByField($data, &#39;age&#39;, $sort);
print_r($data);

&#x2F;&#x2F;这样就得到我们需要的数据
Array
(
    [0] &#x3D;&gt; Array
        (
            [name] &#x3D;&gt; a
            [age] &#x3D;&gt; 10
        )

    [1] &#x3D;&gt; Array
        (
            [name] &#x3D;&gt; c
            [age] &#x3D;&gt; 30
        )

    [2] &#x3D;&gt; Array
        (
            [name] &#x3D;&gt; b
            [age] &#x3D;&gt; 20
        )

    [3] &#x3D;&gt; Array
        (
            [name] &#x3D;&gt; e
            [age] &#x3D;&gt; 50
        )

    [4] &#x3D;&gt; Array
        (
            [name] &#x3D;&gt; d
            [age] &#x3D;&gt; 40
        )

